Odaily Planet Daily News Solana Ecosystem Content Project 10K pre-sale raised a total of 8.23 ​​million US dollars in 24 hours. According to the token economic model, the 10K tokens are distributed as follows: 
60% are allocated to Watch-to-Earn users to incentivize active viewers; 
20% are allocated to pre-sale participants to bind creators and early supporters; 
20% are used to inject liquidity (LP), using a pump.fun-style startup mechanism to maintain a tight spread. 
It is reported that all tokens are deployed on the Solana network, and the SOL raised by the pre-sale will be fully injected into the liquidity pool, with only a 5% platform fee deducted. The pre-sale has ended.
